org.apache.accumulo.core.client.mapreduce

Class RangeInputSplit

  • java.lang.Object
    • InputSplit
      • org.apache.accumulo.core.client.mapreduce.RangeInputSplit
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BatchInputSplit, InputFormatBase.RangeInputSplit, RangeInputSplit

    public class RangeInputSplit
extends InputSplit
    The Class RangeInputSplit. Encapsulates an Accumulo range for use in Map Reduce jobs.
Shall be called with Range, BatchInputSplit.
